ANALYSIS
Thisbill:
I. Establishes a task force to study transmission corridors, EV charging terminals for interstate
trucking,andportelectrification.
II Authorizes a microgrid pilot program to enhance energy resilience and support distributed
energydevelopment.
III. Directs the department of energy to develop cybersecurity guidelines for distributed energy
systems.
